      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，但登录环节要标注一下，我们内部系统用的是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，这个得写清楚。另外访问网站满意度给5分，登录稍微麻烦点给3分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visit website",
        "Log in (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加第一阶段。现在处理浏览阶段：用户滚动首页、查看分类、进入具体分类、应用筛选条件，这些我都按顺序放进来，评分分别是5、3、3、3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Scroll through start page",
        "Check out categories",
